<br />
<br />To be honest what I don't like is when you have to go trough 10 minutes of cut-scenes before being able to play anything. The best is short and breath-taking opening, like in Final Fantasy VII for example.
<br />I also loathe where there is a mandatory tutorial - often I like to experiment things on the fly during gameplay. If you make a tutorial make it either integrated into the story (Fire Emblem GBA) or fully optional.

		

